79
01:02:42,233 --> 01:02:44,533
<b>off pieces of Iran to foreign powers.</b>

80
01:02:45,233 --> 01:02:46,533
<b>Telegraph rights, banking</b>

81
01:02:46,533 --> 01:02:49,366
<b>rights, tobacco rights, oil rights.</b>

82
01:02:50,099 --> 01:02:52,566
<b>Each sale made the Shah more dependent on</b>

83
01:02:52,566 --> 01:02:54,133
