194
01:06:42,233 --> 01:06:44,800
<b>Iranians had just built depended on</b>

195
01:06:44,800 --> 01:06:45,800
<b>controlling concessions.</b>

196
01:06:46,566 --> 01:06:48,833
<b>But Britain and Russia had just divided</b>

197
01:06:48,833 --> 01:06:50,400
<b>up their right to grant</b>

198
01:06:50,400 --> 01:06:51,933
<b>concessions between themselves.</b>

199
01:06:52,433 --> 01:06:53,133
<b>The constitution was</b>

200
01:06:53,133 --> 01:06:55,199
<b>designed to limit foreign influence.</b>

201
01:06:55,599 --> 01:06:56,800
<b>The Anglo-Russian Convention</b>

202
01:06:56,800 --> 01:06:58,733
<b>was designed to guarantee it.</b>

203
01:06:59,166 --> 01:06:59,966
<b>Something had to give.</b>

204
01:07:00,033 --> 01:07:02,833
<b>The new Shah, Mohammed Ali</b>

205
01:07:02,833 --> 01:07:04,233
<b>Shah, saw his opportunity.</b>

206
01:07:05,133 --> 01:07:07,000
<b>The constitution limited his power.</b>

207
01:07:07,766 --> 01:07:09,366
