<b>Colonel Lyakov, the Russian Cossack</b>

216
01:07:28,466 --> 01:07:29,533
<b>commander, to be</b>

217
01:07:29,533 --> 01:07:30,866
<b>military governor of Tehran.</b>

218
01:07:31,400 --> 01:07:33,566
<b>Lyakov sent his Cossacks to occupy the</b>

219
01:07:33,566 --> 01:07:34,866
<b>telegraph office and to</b>

220
01:07:34,866 --> 01:07:36,533
<b>bombard the Majlis building.</b>

221
