227
01:07:50,333 --> 01:07:51,966
<b>divided Iran between themselves.</b>

228
01:07:52,000 --> 01:07:54,566
<b>Foreign intervention and domestic</b>

229
01:07:54,566 --> 01:07:57,233
<b>authoritarianism working together.</b>

230
01:07:57,533 --> 01:08:00,566
<b>About 250 people died. The Majlis</b>

231
01:08:00,566 --> 01:08:01,833
<b>building was destroyed.</b>

232
