526
01:18:31,033 --> 01:18:32,100
<b>The documents prove it.</b>

527
01:18:32,500 --> 01:18:34,066
<b>And the CIA admitted it.</b>

528
01:18:34,066 --> 01:18:36,033
<b>And the trauma this created is real.</b>

529
01:18:36,433 --> 01:18:39,533
<b>After 1953, Iranian politics became</b>

530
01:18:39,533 --> 01:18:41,666
<b>saturated with conspiracy thinking.</b>

531
01:18:42,266 --> 01:18:44,633
<b>Political polemics in Iran are replete</b>

532
01:18:44,633 --> 01:18:45,966
