533
01:18:45,966 --> 01:18:47,966
<b>"Dotayah," "Jazuz," "Hinyat."</b>

534
01:18:48,066 --> 01:18:52,766
<b>These words, plot, spy, treason, became</b>

535
01:18:52,766 --> 01:18:54,166
