552
01:19:26,600 --> 01:19:28,966
<b>So, where does this narrative go wrong?</b>

553
01:19:29,366 --> 01:19:30,866
<b>The coup was foreign planned,</b>

554
01:19:31,166 --> 01:19:32,866
<b>but it was Iranian executed.</b>

555
01:19:33,333 --> 01:19:36,100
<b>The events were steered, executed, and</b>

556
01:19:36,100 --> 01:19:38,266
<b>operationalized by Iranians,</b>

557
01:19:39,000 --> 01:19:40,966
<b>who were directly, and indirectly,</b>

558
01:19:41,533 --> 01:19:44,733
<b>carrying out modified British US plans.</b>

559
01:19:45,333 --> 01:19:47,166
<b>Mossadegh and his colleagues made a</b>

560
01:19:47,166 --> 01:19:48,433
