584
01:20:33,033 --> 01:20:34,966
<b>And the deeper problem is</b>

585
01:20:34,966 --> 01:20:37,033
<b>treating 1953 as the beginning.</b>

586
01:20:37,966 --> 01:20:39,166
<b>As we've seen, the</b>

587
01:20:39,166 --> 01:20:40,833
